The '''1896 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their sixth ever season of organized football. The Keydets had a 3-4 record, marking the first ever losing season in VMI football history.<ref name="VMI">[http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf VMI Football Record Book.qxp<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
